Class JacksonBukkit

java.lang.Object
com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.Module
de.eldoria.jacksonbukkit.JacksonBukkit
All Implemented Interfaces:
Versioned
public class JacksonBukkit extends Module
Class adding support for classes implementing ConfigurationSerializable.
  • Vector
  • BlockVector
  • Color
  • ItemStack
  • PotionEffect
  • FireworkEffect
  • Pattern
  • BoundingBox
  • AttributeModifier
  • Location

It also provides some additional serialization for:

  • NamespacedKey
  • OfflinePlayer
  • Inventory via InventoryWrapper
